---
title: Tex-Mex Chipotle Beef Meatballs  with Creamy Super Slaw
description: Tex-Mex spices and chipotle, sure sounds like a perfect pairing to us. They’re guaranteed to be crowned best flavour combo by
joining beef meatballs in a colourful bowl of slaw. This dish will be going steady in your weekly dinner repertoire for sure.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
